records.name: Canareef Resort Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Herathera, Canareef Resort Maldives is near the airport and on a private beach. Meedhoo Ferry Terminal and Hulhudhoo Harbor are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Mathikilhi Eco Garden and Koagannu Park. Water tubing and swimming offer great chances to get out on the surrounding water, or you can seek out an adventure with ecotours and hiking/biking trails nearby.
descriptions.general: Canareef Resort is on Herathera Island, one of the 6 islands that form Addu Atoll, the Southernmost Atoll in the Maldives. The island is 4.5 km long and narrow with the villas, restaurants, and bars all centrally located towards the middle of the island. Canareef Resort offers experiences suitable for romantic getaways, solo escapes, exciting adventures with friends, or enjoyable family vacations. The Villas are set along the East and West coastline, with the Sunrise Villas on the East, and the Sunset Villas on the West. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk, and free Wi-Fi access throughout the villa and outlets. At the resort, all the rooms along with an Oceanview. have 40-inch LCD televisions, Air-conditioners, Coffee and Tea making facilities, a Minibar, toiletries, and a safety deposit box. The resort consists of 2 restaurants and 3 bars. Kilhi is the main restaurant where Breakfast, Lunch, and Dinner are served in the buffet style. Light meals and drinks are served at the Dhoni Bar. A La Carte dining and drinks are available at the Meera Bar. Snacks and drinks are available at the Beach Bar. Various excursions and water sports are available along with resort-based activities and facilities such as a fully equipped gym, Tennis court, Table tennis, Badminton, Volleyball, Spa, Swimming pool, and Souvenir shop. The resort also has a Kid’s club and Baby-Sitting facility (Surcharge). Honeymooners, Anniversary & Birthday Celebrations: Honeymooners will receive a bottle of wine, fruit basket, and bed decoration in a villa on arrival day. If a guest celebrates a birthday on the island during the stay, a birthday cake and bed decoration will be provided on the birthday. If a guest celebrates their wedding anniversary on the island during their stay, a cake and bed decoration will be provided on the anniversary day.

records.short_description: Excellent wellness hotel. Close to the beach with many options for eating and drinking. Great pool. Beautiful beach.
